# This phrase means without conditions or restrictions, expecting nothing in return
;No strings attached
Ulac asluɣu n lxaṭer


;Firefox is built by a non-profit. That means we can do things that others can’t, like build new products and features without a hidden agenda. We champion your right to privacy with tools like Private Browsing with Tracking Protection, which go beyond what Google Chrome and Microsoft Edge offer.
Firefox tesnulfat-id tuddsa ur yettnadin ara idrimen. Ayagi yemmal-d d akken nezmer ad nexdem ayen urmiren wiyaḍ, am uheggi n ifarisen akked tmahilin imaynuten war ma neffer aqeddic-nneɣ. Tazwart-nneɣ d azref-ik n tbadnit, s ifecka am tunigin tusligt, ammesten mgal aḍfaṛ, iɛeddan ayen i d-isumer Google Chrome neɣ Microsoft Edge.


;What you see is what you get
Ayen tettwalid d ayen ara d-awid


;We believe the Internet is for people, not profit. Unlike other companies, we don’t sell access to your data. <em>You’re</em> in control over who sees your search and browsing history. Choice — that’s what a healthy Internet is all about!
Numen d akken Internet yettwag i yemdanen, mačči i ubaɣur. Ayen iɣ-yessemgaraden d tkebbaniyin-nniḍen, ur neznuzu ara anekcum ar isefka-ik. d <em>KEČČ</em> i d aqeṛṛu ɣef wid ara yewalin umazray-ik n unadi neɣ n tunigin. Ak-nmudd azref ad tfernerḍ — d wa i d Internet uzmir.


;A browser on a mission
Iminig s wazal


;Firefox is a browser with a conscience. As part of the technology non-profit Mozilla, we fight for your online rights, keep corporate powers in check and help educate developing countries on healthy Internet practices. So when you choose Firefox, we’re choosing you, too.
Firefox d iminig yettqadaṛen azalen n timetti. Yebna ɣef tetiknulujit n Mozilla, tuddsa ur yettnadin ara tadrimt. Nseḥbibir ɣef izerfan-ik umḍinen, ad nerwel si tkebbaniyin ur nrewwu ara, ad nmudd afus i tmura tiẓawaliyin ad awin tiktiwin yelhan. Ihi ticki tferneḍ Firefox, am akken d nekni i k-ifernen.


